title: Zombies In Dangerous Dungeon [Action (Shooter), Eng, 2018]
description:
Waking from the cold and opening my eyes, I realize that I am in a wet dungeon or cave. Only rustling wind and droplets of water can be heard.
My whole body is awfully sore and it's so dark I my eyes can barely make out anything. What happened?
I cannot remember anything. Maybe it's just a terrible joke? Suddenly I hear a strange and terrible sound, a sound unlike any other I’ve heard.
A sound that is not produced by any living being… I searched my pockets and found a flashlight. Hooray. It's getting lighter but blood is seeping in. Blood floods your eyes and it’s hard to see what’s going on.
I try to look around as best as I can, but see no exit. And the sounds are getting closer...
